---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Interim/Fractional CXO';
const description = 'Hands-on C-level leadership for scale-ups. CEO, CTO, COO, CRO roles and board member services for critical growth phases.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="py-12 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Interim/Fractional CXO</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Scale-ups face a unique challenge: they need C-level expertise to navigate critical growth phases, but may not need or be able to afford a full-time executive. I provide experienced, hands-on leadership to help companies bridge that gap.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Executive Roles</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-600">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Chief Executive Officer (CEO)</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• Strategic vision and execution</li>
              <li>• Fundraising and investor relations</li>
              <li>• Board management and governance</li>
              <li>• M&A strategy and execution</li>
              <li>• Crisis management and turnarounds</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-600">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Chief Technology Officer (CTO)</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• Technology strategy and roadmap</li>
              <li>• Engineering team leadership</li>
              <li>• Product architecture</li>
              <li>• R&D and innovation initiatives</li>
              <li>• Technical debt management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-600">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Chief Operating Officer (COO)</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• Operational excellence</li>
              <li>• Cross-functional alignment</li>
              <li>• Scalability planning</li>
              <li>• Customer success operations</li>
              <li>• Supply chain management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-600">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Chief Revenue Officer (CRO)</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• Revenue growth strategy</li>
              <li>• Sales and marketing alignment</li>
              <li>• Pricing optimization</li>
              <li>• Customer acquisition & retention</li>
              <li>• Channel strategy</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Board Member Services</h2>
        <p>I provide strategic guidance and governance as a board member for startups and scale-ups:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Strategic planning and oversight</li>
          <li>Financial performance and risk management</li>
          <li>CEO coaching and performance evaluation</li>
          <li>M&A evaluation and execution support</li>
          <li>Investor relations and shareholder value</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">When to Engage</h2>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-semibold mb-3">Ideal Scenarios for Interim/Fractional Executives:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Growth Transition:</strong> Scaling from startup to scale-up (Series A-C)</li>
            <li><strong>Executive Search:</strong> Bridging the gap while recruiting permanent leadership</li>
            <li><strong>Transformation:</strong> Navigating strategic pivots or major change initiatives</li>
            <li><strong>Crisis Management:</strong> Addressing urgent operational or financial challenges</li>
            <li><strong>Special Projects:</strong> Leading complex initiatives (M&A, fundraising, restructuring)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">My Approach</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Rapid Onboarding (Weeks 1-2)</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">Immerse in operations, assess priorities, align with leadership</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Strategic Execution (Months 1-6)</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">Implement quick wins, execute long-term initiatives, build sustainable systems</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Transition Planning (Final Phase)</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">Prepare for permanent leadership, document processes, support successor onboarding</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Track Record</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Wiiisdom (Boston, MA)</strong> - Leadership role driving digital transformation and AI implementation</li>
          <li><strong>SAP Top Talent 2016</strong> - Elite performer recognition</li>
          <li><strong>EMEA Key Contributor Q4 2015</strong> - €3M+ deal</li>
          <li><strong>Winners' Circle 2014-2015</strong> - SAP Global Quota Club</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Engagement Models</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Interim (Full-time)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">3-12 month engagements with full operational responsibility</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Fractional (Part-time)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">1-3 days/week for strategic guidance with selective execution</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Facing a critical growth phase or transition?</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Let's discuss how I can provide the C-level leadership you need to navigate this crucial period.</p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/beaumois/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
            Let's Discuss Your Needs
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
